|GKB-- Silverback -----------------------------------------------|000

Current: |CKBTellurian|000
Command: |CKBsilverback|000
Aliases: |CKBgorilla|000, |CKBsilverbackguardian|000
Guild Level: 21

Silverback calls a massive guardian gorilla out of the Tellurian
current.  The gorilla appears in the room, follows the druid from place
to place, and stays close while growling, pacing, and watching for
incoming blows.

While the guardian remains, it throws itself between the druid and
incoming combat damage.  The druid takes none of the damage from a
blocked hit; the silverback spends its own strength instead.

The silverback has a pool of guardian strength based on Druid guild
level and Silverback training.  The pool also fades naturally over
time, so higher training lets it stay longer and endure more punishment.
When that strength is gone, the gorilla does not die.  It has simply
had enough, and takes off back into the wild current.

The silverback is a protector, not a normal target.  Other players and
creatures cannot attack it directly.
